{"tid":137133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎棟國：兩個警務人員協會言論不代表警方立場","createTime":"2017-02-27T14:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T00:47:40.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3368c1c548a257f6cf756b28273bc47d82d1b340","tid":137133,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"兩個警務人員協會上星期舉行集會。有出席的警務人員發言時自比為「被納粹德軍迫害的猶太人」。德國和以色列駐港總領事館先後發表聲明批評言論不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長黎棟國回應指，警方已與該兩國領事館接觸解釋。黎棟國表示發言人所說的話並不代表警方的立場，而警方亦不認同有關的言論。警隊員佐級協會亦已就事件發表公開聲明表示非常遺憾和難過，希望事情能夠有好的解決。<br />\n<br />\n7名警員因毆打社工曾健超早前被定罪及判監2年。律政司表示，今日收到第2被告劉卓毅、第5被告陳少丹和第6被告關嘉豪，就定罪及刑期提出上訴的上訴通知書。律政司上星期一已收到另外3名被告的上訴申請，而第3被告白榮斌暫時未有提出上訴。"},{"pid":"4f2cfc0e65a3fb1a448b213d2f9803ba8554d3f9","tid":137133,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"7到唔敢睇"},{"pid":"9a1be350fda49742fb5e57579adb80a57f5a64e6","tid":137133,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"棄卒也"},{"pid":"7beb45792016672767e775e903caae3b728a2655","tid":137133,"uid":31658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"Condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e933187db539844c035a09e53615f1be49bc281f","tid":137133,"uid":46277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"警隊員佐級協會亦已就事件發表公開聲明表示非常遺憾和難過，希望事情能夠有好的解決<br />\n<br />\n都係冇道歉<br />\n呀唔係，係死都唔肯道歉<br />\n執法人員連基本打錯就要認打就要企定既態度都唔知<br />\n仲學人執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲成副 「我冇錯」既樣刻撚曬係塊面到<br />\n屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cd3f352a6764695636daeb4cf3dddc4f34156a","tid":137133,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"香港政府同警方高層，似乎回應今次兩國發表聲明批評言論不恰當一事，係用以下實際行動回應.....<br />\n<br />\n1. 對於失言警察同三萬個警察和應「被納粹德軍迫害的猶太人」，與香港政府及警方無關，不會負任何責任<br />\n2. 不會作出道歉，無論失言警察定係政府<br />\n3. 警方高層正式宣佈唔會對失言警察作出處分<br />\n<br />\n如果俾兩個國家人民知道，真係到佢哋出嚟示威反港..........<br />\n<br />\n風波隨時越搞越大......."},{"pid":"9837364a6b57f5b25b34b36b8e9471ffa7c2d1b2","tid":137133,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116bb1446e815078c0eb9b5d001e359c6db3ff98","tid":137133,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3萬個差佬唔代表差佬"},{"pid":"685c0246d49f5ec6a6fd0922a0d6a8f6b199d2f0","tid":137133,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"外交部不代表國家立場"},{"pid":"3a07b960e784abfdfe8b129cc5953abc3510d6d0","tid":137133,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6643703cfd942801a1051cfc9f40c594b04f2640","tid":137133,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:57:27.000Z","msg":"一向都淨係識講個別事件，一個唔代表驚方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11aac25f36a08cc4edbeca6baa28c6db56cdbad8","tid":137133,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:58:12.000Z","msg":"割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5683d0b68e8bcc8c275950da029bee2fadf8ba42","tid":137133,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:59:44.000Z","msg":"做開公墓員真係要學識射波割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4eefd67c9bcaa39310f1c832ff515c9e91fbe8","tid":137133,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:25:40.000Z","msg":"猶差做野唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/f